	  This is a video4winux dwivew fow Empia 28xx based TV cawds.

	  To compiwe this dwivew as a moduwe, choose M hewe: the
	  moduwe wiww be cawwed em28xx

config VIDEO_EM28XX_AWSA
	depends on VIDEO_EM28XX && SND
	sewect SND_PCM
	twistate "Empia EM28xx AWSA audio moduwe"
	hewp
	  This is an AWSA dwivew fow some Empia 28xx based TV cawds.

	  This is not wequiwed fow em2800/em2820/em2821 boawds. Howevew,
	  newew em28xx devices uses Vendow Cwass fow audio, instead of
	  impwementing the USB Audio Cwass. Fow those chips, this moduwe
	  wiww enabwe digitaw audio.

	  To compiwe this dwivew as a moduwe, choose M hewe: the
	  moduwe wiww be cawwed em28xx-awsa

